[00:00.44]	[A room in a castle.,]
[00:01.34]	[Enter HUBERT and Executioners]
[00:02.24]HUBERT	Heat me these irons hot; and look thou stand
[00:05.99]	Within the arras: when I strike my foot
[00:09.37]	Upon the bosom of the ground, rush forth,
[00:12.82]	And bind the boy which you shall find with me
[00:16.72]	Fast to the chair: be heedful: hence, and watch.
