[00:28.71]	Young lad, come forth; I have to say with you.
[00:32.46]	[Enter ARTHUR]
[00:33.36]ARTHUR	Good morrow, Hubert.
[00:35.24]HUBERT	Good morrow, little prince.
[00:37.64]ARTHUR	As little prince, having so great a title
[00:41.16]	To be more prince, as may be. You are sad.
