[00:47.09]ARTHUR	Mercy on me!
[00:48.44]	Methinks no body should be sad but I:
[00:51.66]	Yet, I remember, when I was in France,
[00:54.81]	Young gentlemen would be as sad as night,
[00:58.33]	Only for wantonness. By my christendom,
[01:01.63]	So I were out of prison and kept sheep,
